title: Tax returns of Donald Trump
added: On February 22, 2021, the Supreme Court cleared the way for the New York prosecutor to obtain Trump's tax returns, subject to grand jury secrecy rules that restrict their public release.<ref> [https://edition.cnn.com/2021/02/22/politics/supreme-court-trump-taxes-vance/index.html Supreme Court allows release of Trump tax returns to NY prosecutor]</ref>
